comment: An ounce in a Glencairn glass at the Alibi Room in Vancouver. A nice nose, predominately of vanilla. Peated? Very lightly, I would say.  Quite nice nevertheless.  🤞😉
An ounce in a Glencairn glass at the Alibi Room in Vancouver. A nice nose, predominately of vanilla. Peated? Very lightly, I would say.  Quite nice nevertheless.  🤞😉
Replication of a 1904 whisky. Light, fruity, mild. Unpeated.
